    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The longer you move the faster you will go!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through a wide variety of levels each with their own twist, from fake tiles and cannons to long and challenging runs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is <strong>no time for hesitation</strong>, each level requires you to think and plan ahead whilst maintaining speed and precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race For the Best Score</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045000/extras/43198eb4a43d3a82b236aed64f29fb83.webp?t=1728585952\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the fastest time against friends and the globe in the following modes!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Individual Map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Map Set</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gauntlet</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gain a mastery of the mechanics and find small shortcuts to improve your time on every run through!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difference of even quarter of a second can be crucial to getting the best time possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
